<p>Four-letter -ENT words are invaluable for parallel plays and tight board positions. WENT and VENT both score 7 points thanks to W(4) and V(4), while BENT leverages B(3) for 6 points in just four tiles.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Strategy Tips</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
