    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Hunt Q bingos:</span> EQUIPMENT scores 22 base points plus the 50-point bingo bonus. If you have Q+U+I+P, hold them and look for E+M+N+T to complete the bingo — it's worth the wait.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
